<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>The advanced placement program of the College Entrance Examination Board is accepted by Central Carolina.  In order for credit to be granted a score of 3 or higher must be attained.  An official copy of the score report must be sent to the student records office at Central Carolina Technical College.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.cctech.edu/about/4267.htm" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
